subject: ANN: In Calgary this week
msgSnippet: Everyone: Just an announcement that I m in Calgary AB this week, flying back to Toronto on Friday. If anyone wants to get together or if there are any XP/Agile
messageBody:
Everyone:

Just an announcement that I'm in Calgary AB this week, flying back to Toronto on Friday. If anyone wants to get together or if there are any XP/Agile events or user groups that you think I'd find interesting, then please let me know either by e-mail or by phone. My phone number is in my .sig.

My sincerest apologies if you receive this many times due to being on many mailing lists.

Take care.


J. B. Rainsberger,
President, Diaspar Software Services
